\"share_to_evernote_submit_button\" class=\"submit\" value=\"Post to Evernote\"/>\\n<a href=\"javascript:void(0);\" class=\"cancel_box\">cancel</a>\\n</div>\\n</form>\\n</div>\\n</div>\\n</div>\\n<!-- Article Title / Metadata overlay that shows up on scroll -->\\n<aside id=\"left_context_metadata\" class=\"js_control_bar_recall left_context_metadata\" aria-hidden=\"true\">\\n<div class=\"metadata\">\\n<header>What Happens When Two Bankers and an Engineer Get a Billion Dollars?</header>\\n\\n<div class=\"source\">\\n<div class=\"site_name\">\\n<a class=\"original\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com/news/features/2017-02-16/global-infrastructure-partners-gets-big-returns-in-sleepy-sector\">bloomberg.com</a>\\n</div>\\n\\n<div class=\"site_domain\">\\n<a class=\"original\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com/news/features/2017-02-16/global-infrastructure-partners-gets-big-returns-in-sleepy-sector\">Bloomberg</a>\\n</div>\\n\\n</div>\\n\\n\\n<time class=\"meta_read_time\" aria-hidden=\"true\">\\n1 min<span class=\"remainder\"> remaining</span>\\n</time>\\n\\n</div>\\n\\n</aside>\\n</section>\\n<section id=\"swap_logo_capital\" class=\"js_control_bar_recall swap_logo_capital\">\\n<aside class=\"logo_capital\"></aside>\\n</section>\\n<section id=\"recall_indicator\" class=\"recall_indicator\">\\n<a href=\"javascript:void(0);\" class=\"js_control_bar_recall\">\\n<span class=\"ipicon ipicon-ellipsis\"></span>\\n</a>\\n</section>\\n</nav>\\n\\n</div>\\n</div>\\n<div class=\"container read_content_container\">\\n<main class=\"main\" aria-label=\"Article\">\\n\\n<div class=\"badge-container read-tag-container js_read_tag_container\"></div>\\n<div id=\"titlebar\" class=\"titlebar\">\\n<h1>What Happens When Two Bankers and an Engineer Get a Billion Dollars?</h1>\\n<span class=\"origin_line\">\\n\\n<a class=\"original\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com/news/features/2017-02-16/global-infrastructure-partners-gets-big-returns-in-sleepy-sector\">Bloomberg</a>\\n\\n&middot;\\n\\nby <span class=\"author\">Jason Kelly</span>\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n</span>\\n\\n</div>\\n<div id=\"story\"data-id=\"870174254\" data-words=\"123\" class=\"story\">\\n<article><div><div><div><a href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com/business?source=eyebrow\">Business</a></div><div>Markets Magazine</div></div><div><div><p>Global Infrastructure Partners turned a sleepy sector into one that has investors clamoring for more.</p>\\n</div></div></div><div><div><div><div><div><div><div><div><div>By </div></div></div><div><div><div><time>February 16, 2017 at 12:01 AM EST</time></div><span>Updated on  <div><time>February 16, 2017 at 1:28 PM EST</time></div></span></div></div></div></div><div><p>Bill Woodburn<strong> </strong>showed up for dinner as a courtesy.</p><p>It was 2006, and the former head of General Electric\\xe2\\x80\\x99s infrastructure business and Jack Welch prot\\xc3\\xa9g\\xc3\\xa9 had made up his mind to turn down Adebayo Ogunlesi and Matt Harris, the pair of former Credit Suisse bankers who\\xe2\\x80\\x99d invited him for Chinese food. Instead of joining their nascent fund, the sought-after Woodburn was taking a job with Steve Schwarzman\\xe2\\x80\\x99s Blackstone.</p></div><div><a href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com/tips/\"><div>Have a confidential tip for our reporters? <span>Get in Touch</span></div></a><a href=\"http://bloom.bg/dg-ws-core-bcom-m1\"><div><div>Before it\\xe2\\x80\\x99s here, it\\xe2\\x80\\x99s on the <span>Bloomberg Terminal</span></div><div> LEARN MORE</div></div></a></div></div></div></div></div></article>\\n</div>\\n<footer id=\"footer\" class=\"footer\">\\n<span class=\"origin_line\">\\n\\n<a class=\"original\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com/news/features/2017-02-16/global-infrastructure-partners-gets-big-returns-in-sleepy-sector\">Bloomberg</a>\\n\\n&middot;\\n\\nby <span class=\"author\">Jason Kelly</span>\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n</span>\\n</footer>\\n<!-- ### Parser\\nInstaparser\\n-->\\n</main>\\n</div>\\n<!-- Modals -->\\n<div id=\"modal_backer\" class=\"modal_ba